snippet.title: Space Beret Trailer
snippet.description: The year is 4207. Over a thousand years ago humanity started drastically expanding over the known universe not to relay only on the overpopulated and irreversibly polluted Earth. Common Earth government called United Earth was formed, and a scientific society ushering a new age prospered. Wars no longer plagued mankind united in the exploration of various galaxies. For a long time humans thought they were alone, they were wrong.
